(6988, 'Kokast 4mg 7 chewable tab.', 'كوكاست 4مجم 7 اقراص مضغ', '27', '37', 'Montelukast', 'Egyphar', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '', 'Asthma.anti-inflammatory.leukotriene antagonist', '4mg', 'Montelukast is indicated for:
